Kansas City population data sets

population.Rd

Kansas City, Missouri population data sourced from the US Census Bureau's decennial census and American Community Survey (ACS). 1-year ACS data is available at the city geographic level only. 5-year ACS data is available at the city, census tract, and ZCTA geographic levels.
